# Recommendations

* When creating test records, including in the name “Test” with the UAT Test Number for easy reference  
* Use BH Record ID on any HubSpot object to locate the right record in BH.  
* Use Table Views above and configure and save a new custom view during your own testing, to see only the properties & records you are concerned with  
* We have added BH Record ID as global searchable fields.  
* It is useful to locate in HubSpot the associated object ID from Bullhorn both as confirmation that Pipedream sync has completed the association on its most recent 10 minute cycle, but also to locate the correct record in Bullhorn.   
* Sandbox tends to sync on ‘the 3s’  
* A test user is especially useful when configuring & testing page views. If you have a second computer logged in as the test user this process becomes more efficient.
